include ../../components/rounded-button/rounded-button

section(class="feedback")
  div(class="container")
    div(class="heading-wrapper")
      h3(class="title-text") Trusted by Thousands of Happy Customers
      p These are the stories of our customers who have joined us with great pleasure when using this crazy feature.
    div(class="swiper-container mySwiper")
      ul(class="swiper-wrapper")
        li(class="swiper-slide")
          div(class="user")
            div(class="user-info")
              picture
                source(srcset="img/person-1.webp" type="image/webp")
                img(src="img/person-1.png", alt="User-Avatar")
              div
                p Viezh Robert
                p Warsaw, Poland
            div(class="user-rate")
              p 4,5
              include ../../../img/svg/star.svg
          div(class="user-text")
            p “Wow... I am very happy to use this VPN, it turned out to be more than my expectations and so far there have been no problems. LaslesVPN always the best”.

        li(class="swiper-slide")
          div(class="user")
            div(class="user-info")
              picture
                source(srcset="img/person-2.webp" type="image/webp")
                img(src="img/person-2.png", alt="User-Avatar")
              div
                p Yessica Christy
                p Shanxi, China
            div(class="user-rate")
              p 4,5
              include ../../../img/svg/star.svg
          div(class="user-text")
            p “I like it because I like to travel far and still can connect with high speed.”.

        li(class="swiper-slide")
          div(class="user")
            div(class="user-info")
              picture
                source(srcset="img/person-3.webp" type="image/webp")
                img(src="img/person-3.png", alt="User-Avatar")
              div
                p Kim Young Jou
                p Seoul, South Korea
            div(class="user-rate")
              p 4,5
              include ../../../img/svg/star.svg
          div(class="user-text")
            p “This is very unusual for my business that currently requires a virtual private network that has high security.”.
